備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
■ 語言文字與域外漢文資料之深入研究
 To cultivate the capabilities for in-depth research of materials in Chinese literature from home and abroad.
□ 傳統學術領域與現代學術領域之獨立研究
 To cultivate the ability to conduct independent research of traditional and modern academics.
□ 中西文學與文化理論之比較分析
 To cultivate the ability to compare and analyze Chinese and western literary theories.
□ 探討傳統學術思想的現代意義與發展
 To explore the modern interpretations and developments of traditional academic thoughts.
 

核心能力 Competence
■ 具備語言文字研究之能力
 To cultivate the proficiency in language research.
□ 培養獨立研究傳統與現代學術之能力
 To cultivate the ability to conduct independent research of traditional and modern academics.
□ 培養中外文學與文化理論之能力
 To increase the knowledge of Chinese/foreign literature and cultural theory
□ 培養文學鑑賞與經典詮釋之能力
 To cultivate the capabilities for appreciation and interpretation of Chinese literary works and classics.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       訓練研究生撰寫有關詩學論文時應思考的各種角度。This course will aim itself at introducing the literary features of western and Chinese master pieces, covering poems, short stories and films. The attention is also paid to the critical essays written in English on modern Chinese Literature. The objective is to enable the students to understand and enjoy western literature and to read critical essays on Chinese literature.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
能概括瞭解西方漢學傳統、當代美國東亞研究、漢學研究之著名大師與學術流派。從選讀漢學家著作及現代中國文學領域之期刊論文，獲得西方研究關註之議題。能具備基本英文摘要撰寫能力與學術研究方法之嘗試。 

